OL,3,CPayment machines vandalised on the day
OL,4,Ccharges were introduced at car park
OL,6,FNew payment machines installed at a
OL,7,Fcar park in Helston, Cornwall have
OL,8,Fbeen vandalised on the day charges
OL,9,Fwere due to be introduced.
OL,11,FFoam was sprayed into the slots for
OL,12,Fmoney and the ticket dispenser. All
OL,13,Fthree machines in the car park were
OL,14,Ftargeted and have been taken out of
OL,15,Fuse.
OL,17,FThe machines had only just been
OL,18,Finstalled as part of Cornwall
OL,19,FCouncil's plan to introduce charges at
OL,20,Fthe Fairground Car Park, which had
OL,21,Fpreviously been free to use.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
