OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782908304
OL,3,CPayment machines vandalised on the day
OL,4,Ccharges were introduced at car park
OL,6,FIn a statement the council said: "We
OL,7,Fare disappointed by the vandalism that
OL,8,Fhas taken place in Helston this
OL,9,Fweekend, the cost of such repairs
OL,10,Fimpact the taxpayer directly.
OL,12,F"We will be putting signs up advising
OL,13,Fthat charges still apply, and payments
OL,14,Fmust be made via the JustPark App
OL,15,Fwhile the machines are repaired.
OL,17,F"A police investigation into the
OL,18,Fdamage is underway. Anyone with any
OL,19,Finformation is asked to contact Devon
OL,20,Fand Cornwall Police on 101."
OL,26,@nD@bOUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782908304
OL,3,CPayment machines vandalised on the day
OL,4,Ccharges were introduced at car park
OL,6,FITV News West Country spoke to people
OL,7,Fusing the car park and most weren't
OL,8,Fsurprised at the vandalism because of
OL,9,Fthe strength of feeling locally about
OL,10,Fthe introduction of parking charges.
OL,12,FAndrew Emery parked his car there
OL,13,Ftoday (June 30) and said: "I think
OL,14,Fit's a shame the council have decided
OL,15,Fto go for the option of parking
OL,16,Fmeters, as far as we are aware the
OL,17,Fground is owned by the people of
OL,18,FHelston, it was gifted to them.
OL,26,@uD@[OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782908304
OL,3,CPayment machines vandalised on the day
OL,4,Ccharges were introduced at car park
OL,6,F"There was a lot of opposition to the
OL,7,Foption of going for the parking
OL,8,Fmeters, I don't really approve of the
OL,9,Fvandalism but I understand why people
OL,10,Ffeel aggrieved about it."
OL,12,FMonica Hancock, who lives just outside
OL,13,FHelston, said: "I don't think they
OL,14,Fshould have been installed anyway. I
OL,15,Fthink they should have listened to
OL,16,Fwhat people were saying and they
OL,17,Fshould have taken into account how
OL,18,Fimportant this place is to different
OL,19,Fpeople.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@YO]uD@POU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782908304
OL,3,CPayment machines vandalised on the day
OL,4,Ccharges were introduced at car park
OL,6,F"Everybody who comes here would have a
OL,7,Fstory to tell of why it is so
OL,8,Fimportant to them. I am just one of
OL,9,Fthose people. I don't agree with
OL,10,Fvandalism, but nobody's been hurt,
OL,11,Fsomeone's quietly resisted, come and
OL,12,Fsaid that's it."
OL,26,@tD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
