PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782908304
OL,3,CPayment machines vandalised on the day
OL,4,Ccharges were introduced at car park
OL,6,FLucy Grant, who works in Helston,
OL,7,Fsaid: "I can understand there's a lot
OL,8,Fof public feeling against the charges,
OL,9,FI don't think I would recommend people
OL,10,Fvandalise them but it was debated
OL,11,Fquite quickly and it's all been
OL,12,Fimplemented very quickly and there's a
OL,13,Flot of unhappy feeling about the
OL,14,Fcosts."
OL,16,FThe new charges run from 9am until
OL,17,F4pm, although the first hour is free.
OL,26,@oD@GO]vD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
