OL,3,CPayment machines vandalised on the day
OL,4,Ccharges were introduced at car park
OL,6,FWhen the plans were announced there
OL,7,Fwas opposition with the Town Council
OL,8,Fobjecting with concerns over the
OL,9,Fimpact on residents, visitors,
OL,10,Fcommunity wellbeing, and the local
OL,11,Feconomy.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
